== Intent ==

Database and SQL-based approach with [[Technology:MySQL]]

== Languages ==

* [[Language:SQL]]


== Technologies ==

* [[Technology:MySQL]]
* [[Technology:XAMPP]]: provide of MySQL (Version 1.7.3)
* [[Technology:MySQL Workbench]]: query browser (Version 5.2.33)

== Usage ==

We use SQL for data processing.
We exercise some company scenarios.
This project is entirely SQL/scripting-based.

We need a local database Server.
In the following we explain the steps for XAMPP.  
http://www.apachefriends.org/en/xampp.html

We also need some SQL tool.
In the following we explain the steps for MySQL Workbench.
http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/workbench/

* Download and install XAMPP. 
* Open the "XAMPP Control Panel" and start "Apache" and "Mysql".
* A local MySQL Server is now running.
 * Server Host : "localhost"
 * Port : 3306
 * Username : "root"
 * Password : "" (no password)
* Connect to database in MySQL Workbench.
* Select "test" database or create one.
* Create tables (run SQL script Company.sql)
* Populate tables (run SQL script sampleCompany.sql)
* Execute scenario total (run SQL script Total.sql)
* Execute scenario cut (run SQL script Cut.sql)
* Execute scenario total, again (run SQL script Total.sql)
 
